EBA Has ‘Central Role’ Regarding Bank-Crisis Response, EU Says

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-10-05T10:50:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/eba-has-central-role-regarding-bank-crisis-response-eu-says.html
The European Banking Authority has a
“central role” regarding the region’s response to the
difficulties facing lenders, EU spokesman  Amadeu Altafaj  said
today.  Government help for lenders in trouble needs to be “in
perfect conformity with state aid regulations,” he added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
